NAME
    arcfind - The archival file finder.

  arcfind
    The main subroutine. Opens the dir, reads the files, sorts them, then
    selects the which ones we actually want.

    Parameters: $dir: The directory we want the files from. $minFiles: The
    minimum number of files to leave. $maxAge: The maximum age of the files
    to leave. $inverse: (Boolean) Set if you want inverse output.

